1. Install:
  emerge xscreensaver rxvt-unicode feh liberation-fonts alsa-mixer dmenu xdotool scrot

2. Copy files:
  .xinitrc -> ~/.xinitrc
  .Xresources -> ~/.Xresources
  xmonad.hs.example -> xmonad.hs
  xmobar.hs.example -> xmobar.hs

3. Change xmonad.hs and xmobar.hs

4. Compile:
  xmonad --recompile && xmonad --restart
